  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/427d54b1001001545f64a61ced04a999.avif?t=1772418159\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The religious city of Logres. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a city that worships the Goddess of Fortune, an angel descends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her name is Zerachiel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zerachiel struggles to rescue her comrades who are imprisoned by the cult, but she is defeated and stripped of her powers by a girl claiming to be a saint... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weeks later, Zerachiel, discarded like trash and set free, decides to take revenge on the cult, unaware that fate had already taken a significant turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tapestry of intersecting destinies and a drama of many lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/d9a0820fc86f0a5355435f4f39f3b19b.avif?t=1772418159\" width=616 height=280 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/8933ee442104320662fe6a8e407ad442.avif?t=1772418159\" width=616 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/134ebc2169fd3d61db319fecb74067d5.avif?t=1772418159\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This work is a turn-based battle JRPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player controls Zerachiel and her companions to fight against enemies and uncover the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/6ec1ad5d89e01ee565df7b5a4b496a0e.avif?t=1772418159\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adopts CTB (Charge Turn Battle), allowing actions in the order of highest agility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons can be enhanced</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random dungeons available</p></li></ul>",
