"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804550/extras/6ec1ad5d89e01ee565df7b5a4b496a0e.avif?t=1772418159\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adopts CTB (Charge Turn Battle), allowing actions in the order of highest agility</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons can be enhanced</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random dungeons available</p></li></ul>",
